{"tid":2227922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登：特朗普確診顯示戴口罩比做「硬漢」更重要","createTime":"2020-10-03T07:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T07:27:42.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f90b45478b5ed957bbbfa899925f2649753bb68f","tid":2227922,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">咁你之前又一戴一露？</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普確診新型肺炎入院，檢測結果呈陰性的競選對手，民主黨總統候選人拜登表示，特朗普確診顯示要認真看待疫情大流行，並告訴美國民眾，戴口罩比做一個「硬漢」更重要。<br />\n<br />\n拜登繼續造勢活動，到了密歇根州拉票。他說，與太太祈禱，希望特朗普和第一夫人梅拉尼婭早日康復。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">他在演講全程戴著口罩，有別與以往在講話前除低口罩。</span></span></strong>拜登說，這不是政治問題，提醒所有人必須認真對待疫情，它不會自動消失，敦促所有美國人戴口罩，經常洗手並保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552883-20201003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552883-20201003.htm&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=b5077207\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552883-20201003.htm&h=594b6736\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552883-20201003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"28f3cd2383f5c7874ecbc204381182f8a24d97d3","tid":2227922,"uid":85629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"登登在小孩面前更加成為硬漢"},{"pid":"4b2cc2b583ddc3d4ca94b767eb7ab717e16dd64d","tid":2227922,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f3cd2383f5c7874ecbc204381182f8a24d97d3","tid":2227922,"uid":85629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"登登在小孩面前更加成為硬漢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\